text:
Hey all, I wanted to tell you about our new app, *<https://app.HubSpot.com/l/ecosystem/marketplace/apps/_detail/sequential-powered-by-unmatched-1967082|Sequential>*!

It's designed to create easy numbers for HubSpot. For example, numbering deals such as UNM-001, UMN-002... etc.

Or you could number tickets... SUP001, SUP002 etc.

Keen for your thoughts! :boom:

<https://app.HubSpot.com/l/ecosystem/marketplace/apps/_detail/sequential-powered-by-unmatched-1967082>
